{"tid":1513190,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"特首推出新的惡法-- 但是香港人可以對付那個惡法","createTime":"2019-08-28T08:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T08:22:37.000Z","uid":268924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4cc8fa8b2cbdf907ede7dd0af305257101472abb","tid":1513190,"uid":268924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:21:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=28479860\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D28479860&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5MtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=d6cf2870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=28479860</a><br />\n<br />\n緊急法 ,Cap 241<br />\n第二節--Power to make regulations<br />\n。。On any occasion which the Chief Executive in Council may consider to be an  occasion of emergency or public danger he may make any regulations whatsoever which  he may consider desirable in the public interest.<br />\n=======<br />\n據悉，這是湯家驊對 鄭月娥 最新的法律建議。<br />\n======我的評論：<br />\nCap241 可能是違憲【參詳 基本法第48條，56條】，違反香港人權法 【the Bill of rights】, 違反 ICCPR 。<br />\n昨天我說了，關於 堪輿學 與 湯家驊 ；<br />\n我希望香港人【包括政客】好運。"},{"pid":"ecb2dbc527688b4c0a6f4de21bc79205109dcc57","tid":1513190,"uid":99183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mOhUStr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmOhUStr.gif&h=ab18dc93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5MtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=7e371aa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5MtNvD6oN5